@node History "History"

V0.2ß   5-Apr-99 After some feedback a few bugs have been
        fixed, a couple of new features have been added
        and alot of stuff have been added to the TODO.

        ° Made saving safe(r) (MP)

        ° Added a progressbar when loading guides.

        ° If only one guide is loaded, it does not need
          to be selected for a save/kill operation.

        ° Put back parsing of styles etc. when loading.

        ° Changed all the toolbars to Toolbar.mcc by 
          Benny Kjćr Nielsen. Some of the new gadget-
          images are stolen from Bennys Toolbar arc-
          hive, some are drawn by me. Benny's looks
          pretty good, but mine sucks :)

        ° Fixed the non updating nodelist when changing
          nodenames. (MP)
    

V0.1ß   94-Mar-99, Second release, still an unfinnished
        product.
        I just released this, because I know a couple
        of people out there are using the previous ver-
        sion, and they might want the bugfixes.

        Still didnt start the WYSIWYG class.

        ° The 'changes made' image wouldnt update after
          a save, FIXED.

        ° The 'save' function would sometimes forget to
          add a '/' between the path and the filename.

        ° The texteditor will use it's fixed font (if one
          is specified in mui prefs, anyway)
          This should be make it easier to edit guides,
          since they are normally displayd with a fixed font.

        ° Compiled for 68000 and with optimizing on,
          mostly for fun.

V0.0ß    First release. Prerelease of a pretty unfinnished product.
@ENDNODE

